	 /Cex exch def
	 currentfont Ratio scalefont setfont
	 /Pch-x Pch-x Ratio mul def
	 /Pch-y Pch-y Ratio mul def
	 /Text-y Text-y Ratio mul def}bd
/So{4 1 roll exch 4 -1 roll Plot astore pop SetClip}bd
